{"tid":1711031,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其他大學同我聽住！以後唔再談判！！！","createTime":"2019-11-12T09:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T10:13:36.000Z","uid":134093,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2274ac2edf8e4ca59fa2f0cd101166ecfc1f7970","tid":1711031,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mry4gAR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMry4gAR.png&h=c8498dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n談你老母"},{"pid":"6a9d7455e95a3c382de7ee4fd592ddc33bdf7c74","tid":1711031,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:39:57.000Z","msg":"⚠轉出去⚠<br />\n❗大學 Lab 善用化學品反抗❗<br />\n❗HNO3❗<br />\n❗Mg❗<br />\n❗NH4NO3❗<br />\n❗NaOH❗<br />\n❗ANFO❗<br />\n❗ANSU❗"},{"pid":"cc84afaab16d27d8e3f06b624c79024aac5e6716","tid":1711031,"uid":33586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:53:09.000Z","msg":"正視聽 無同學想談判<br />\n<br />\n【突發】認住你呢個出賣中大的人。<br />\n<br />\n今日香港中文大學二號橋環迴東路，中文大學傳訊及公共關係處處長張宏艷表示和警察商討後，防暴警察願意將防線退後至二號橋更亭，另五名警察會留在橋上。警察也希望學生不會推前防線。<br />\n<br />\n結果不到一分鐘，警方立即反口，以催淚彈狂轟中大，守軍奮力抵抗。短短數分鐘，警方無間斷發出催淚彈及慢慢推進。<br />\n<br />\n明明講好左數，點解會出事？我一google個名就馬上發現，屌你原來講數果件張宏艷藍絲黎，寫過文章blame手足。仆你個街，而家黑狗打入私人地方，學生比人捉，就係因為你叫同學退防啊。你點交待屌你？日防夜防，家賊難防<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/column/article/2458096/%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%A4%B1%E6%B0%91%E5%BF%83?fbclid=IwAR3fQcH5fXuOM185WbGpet1GH697vUKbtW3YK0jKRiQbBFIeRwi2WGBHKKw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F2458096%2F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BF%2583%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3fQcH5fXuOM185WbGpet1GH697vUKbtW3YK0jKRiQbBFIeRwi2WGBHKKw&d=9CaroZtPfqcCLVRp0XVEkWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=394d31a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/column/article/2458096/%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E5%A4%B1%E6%B0%91%E5%BF%83?fbclid=IwAR3fQcH5fXuOM185WbGpet1GH697vUKbtW3YK0jKRiQbBFIeRwi2WGBHKKw</a>"},{"pid":"97d12b847f19d355313de96da84c8108c4e58e0d","tid":1711031,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">趁而家仲有時間, 全港各間大學的手足, 最好立即撤離宿舍, 當然不要留下不利證據。走唔到都唔一定要守, 消滅所有不利的證據, 最好影定自己房的相, CALL定律師, 防止被屈<br />\n<br />\n千祁唔好死守校園!!!!!! 無謂製造壯烈犧牲畫面比對家提高士氣</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e0ae3c44f3335868987f23859509e6a8e60a83bf","tid":1711031,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:55:31.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"4616159d15e933365c8ecb47a47bd994a9408674","tid":1711031,"uid":74763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"14年扮送飯運軍火之後，仲信警察既都要反省下。"},{"pid":"529d898d145cc45b36100d409b76696fb0730d98","tid":1711031,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd78afc4f6bfbd253811e399fe6aeca4ea2f78dc","tid":1711031,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj